{"tid":1425216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【簡單易明文宣】光復香港 時代革命 背後意思","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:57:43.000Z","uid":280436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd567d643eee47be565f9b565a1b951612482b39","tid":1425216,"uid":280436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"文宣組！！！！<br />\n宜家林鄭要格硬扣港獨嘅帽子俾我地示威者<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老屈</span>我地 帶領風向<br />\n我地就更加要表明 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span> 嘅真正意思<br />\n係要改革社會結構呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n原post：<br />\n唔敢代表大家，但希望得倒大家認同<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7SeWA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7SeWA6.jpg&h=9f504a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuPwYPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuPwYPs.jpg&h=b5f0a0f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上圖片話比大家聽讀設計嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fb54aa16d585c9bc2b007ab8b672f421a94725","tid":1425216,"uid":280436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"【簡單易明文宣】光復香港 時代革命 背後意思<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"813b1fc95723bee78c37a4c02b13e306d80fe1c4","tid":1425216,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"簡潔易明<br />\n思路都正確，我個人認同<br />\n但要諗諗點樣唔俾人偷改圖"},{"pid":"f4d7aca0939b051067adf7fcb22c7a9e5348d9fa","tid":1425216,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"其中一個方向係<br />\n正名「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n光復香港 = 回復以往繁榮既香港<br />\n方法: 首4大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n時代革命=香港體制要改革<br />\n方法: 第五大訴求<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而唔係林鄭所誤解既港獨<br />\n<br />\n建議之一, 請其他巴打更改<br />\n<br />\n重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a>"}]}